{"tid":1651961,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"推上熱門  只有公開CCTV先會知到真相","createTime":"2019-10-13T13:44:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-13T15:23:21.000Z","uid":160499,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"9bfae72b1cd613f55c2bf99d614f0f6c935e16e0","tid":1651961,"uid":160499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T13:44:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GJDGMPX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGJDGMPX.jpg&h=a5dbbb92&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n懇請各位街坊於星期一早上8:30到調景嶺HKDI地下聲援眾學生，要求VTC:<br />\n<br />\n1. 公開陳彥霖同學於失蹤當日(9月19日)的閉路電視(CCTV)片段<br />\n2. 交代陳彥霖同學的失物，是由何人(途人，學生或職員)以及何位置執拾交還校方<br />\n<br />\n務必要還陳彥霖同學一個真相<br />\n<br />\n如果VTC未能於星期一中午12:30前回覆上述訴求，將會有進一步行動<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y1QmMP5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY1QmMP5.jpg&h=eea9e98c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FH4rdu7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFH4rdu7.jpg&h=571ad4e4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sbJSTvb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsbJSTvb.jpg&h=379f924c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dsM9bgW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdsM9bgW.jpg&h=88e9a5d8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OReyCWX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOReyCWX.jpg&h=fba67ae4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔可以比陳同學死得不明不白</span></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"194b29f4c3de907782d3cb6100c0ebc7cb92991a","tid":1651961,"uid":160499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T13:44:34.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"878dd934d3d5e762869f0a23a0594f2256cfcbc8","tid":1651961,"uid":160499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime